    "description": "Project Eternal是一款以科幻机械风格作为题材的卡牌构筑类塔防游戏<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2270630/extras/edab6c5ab348a99af43dda0e022d5717.poster.avif?t=1673573184\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2270630/extras/edab6c5ab348a99af43dda0e022d5717.webm?t=1673573184\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2270630/extras/edab6c5ab348a99af43dda0e022d5717.mp4?t=1673573184\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>·独特的建造机制<br>  不同于以往的塔防游戏，玩家需要通过抽取卡牌的方式来建造炮塔。<br>  积攒洗牌能量条，并在合适的时机刷新所拥有的炮塔设计图。<br>  炮塔的设计图在每次被刷新后只能建造一次，谨慎考虑炮塔放置的地点。<br>  通过击败来袭的敌人获得相应颜色的资源。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2270630/extras/3184f7c65e70281c0b43ad8f8bdf4c37.poster.avif?t=1673573184\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2270630/extras/3184f7c65e70281c0b43ad8f8bdf4c37.webm?t=1673573184\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2270630/extras/3184f7c65e70281c0b43ad8f8bdf4c37.mp4?t=1673573184\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>·动态构建的牌组<br>  在通关每一个关卡后，可以从作为奖励的科研成果箱中抽取新的炮塔设计图。<br>  选择它们加入你的牌组，通过组合和搭配，来让牌组发挥力量，打败敌人、挑战Boss。<br><br><br>·操控战术设施来协助防御<br>  导弹，冷冻激光，亦或者是卫星射线<br>  在未来的更新中玩家可以使用收集到的资源来购买强大的防御设施。<br>  他们虽然昂贵且使用次数有限，但使用得当的话，一击便可扭转战局。",
